The truth about Ona’s DNA is finally out on House of Zwide. The man she thought was her boss, Funani Zwide, is her biological dad. Years ago, Isaac decided to save Ona from the fire he started after Funani’s wife, Faith, manipulated him into killing Ona’s mum. Isaac then raised her as his own. It’s all thanks to Zwide’s son, Nkosi, that the truth is out. He started having nightmares about that night and told his dad, who stole Ona’s hairbrush and sent it for DNA testing. ALSO READ :BBMzansi star gets her moment to shine The whole situation is sad because Ona is the reason Isaac turned away from crime. On Uzalo, Lillyworks as a cop but she’s always borrowing money and is drowning in debt. Her aunt MaDongwe confides in her boyfriend, General, and he calls a family meeting. It doesn’t end well! Someone needs to remind Hector on The Queen that he’s married. He wants to play happy family with Vuyiswa and their baby, and even asked for amalove back. They’ve had tlof tlof and there’s no turning back.